reviewText: It broke in the machine. I'm sending  it back

The most beautiful Mass that I have found on tape yet.  The schola for the High Mass is breathtaking.  Includes also a low Mass (Latin)
that lasts abput 35 minutes and Benediction.

Very good quality tape - true to the quality detailed on Amazon.

A visual exposition of a Holy Mass that was once universal. The written booklet accompanying the tape allows one to follow the ceremonies.
